<h2>Compound Interest Formula</h2>

<p class="table-big-formula">
Starting Capital * (1 + Interest/100)<sup>Years</sup>
</p>

<h2>Future Value of an Annuity Formula</h2>

<p class="table-big-formula">
    (Monthly Contribution * 12) * ((1 + Interest/100)<sup>Years</sup>-1)/(Interest/100)
</p>

<h2>This Calculator Formula</h2>

<p>
    Compound Interest Formula + Future Value of an Annuity Formula
</p>

<p class="table-big-formula">
    Starting Capital * (1 + Interest/100)<sup>Years</sup> + (Monthly Contribution * 12) * ((1 + Interest/100)<sup>Years</sup>-1)/(Interest/100)
    </p>

